<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.168876>
    dc:description "FIGURES 1 – 7: 1 – 3 Maladera infuscata (Moser, 1915) (Lectotype: “ Korea ”); 4 – 7: Maladera howdeni sp. n. (Holotype: Taiwan, Wushe); 1, 3, 4, 7: aedeagus, lateral view; 2: aedeagus, dorsal view; 5: parameres, dorsal view; 6: parameres, ventral view. Scale: 0.5 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation <https://zenodo.org/record/168876/files/figure.png> ;
    a fabio:Figure .
